For 3 years EMIR TRAVEL AGENCY has been providing an unrivalled full spectrum of business and leisure travel services that our satisfied customers will certainly attest to. We pride ourselves in offering world class service in the regions we operate. Our well experienced consultants offer clients with most economical, practical and convenient travel solutions. EMIR TRAVEL AGENCY was registered in the year 2016 and has received numerous awards and recognitions since date. We have established a reputation in the industry for having strong and long lasting relationships with both our suppliers and clients.

EMIR TRAVEL AGENCY has received notable recognition during this year KPMG Top 100 Mid-sized Company Awards for 2017-2018 We have spread our distribution network through the opening of the EMIR TRAVEL AGENCY in Nairobi branch; the first in town in 2017 and other branch in 2018.
